  <summary date="2015-05-19T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Facilitating Investments in Local Markets Act or the FILM Act

Amends the Internal Revenue Code, with respect to the expensing of the costs of qualified film and television productions, to: (1) extend through 2016 provisions allowing such expensing, and (2) allow such expensing for the costs of certain live theatrical productions.</summary>
